title: #168 - Jerry Rocha & ME
description: Comedian Jerry Rocha and I hang out in the Mancave & talk about working the Laff Stop in Houston, his start in comedy, the guys he saw stall due to drugs and alcohol, growing up in an apartment, and moving to LA.
